com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.outputs

Class ShardingOutputWriter<K,V,WriterT extends OutputWriter<KeyValue<K,V>>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.OutputWriter<KeyValue<K,V>>
      • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.outputs.ShardingOutputWriter<K,V,WriterT>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - key type
    V - value type
    WriterT - type of the output writer being written to
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GoogleCloudStorageMapOutputWriter

    public abstract class ShardingOutputWriter<K,V,WriterT extends OutputWriter<KeyValue<K,V>>>
extends OutputWriter<KeyValue<K,V>>
    Writes KeyValues out to a number of output writers each corresponding to a different shard A sharder and an Output object are provided in the constructor. The output object will be used to create the writers that will be written to. The sharder will determine which writer any given record will be written to based on the key.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
